Directory descriptions:

configfiles: configuration input files. 
documentation: project and scientific information.
include: directory for header files. Currently contains bgtypes.h, used to switch between single and double-precision floating point
legacy-code: previous versions of BrainGrid/Liquid State Machine/CSIM/etc
MATLAB: Matlab post-processing for output files
Matrix: Vector and 2D matrix classes
Mersenne: unused
paramcontainer: cmdline parser
results: output files and matlab plots
RNG: random number generator
scripts: shell scripts for building different simulator versions
SourceVersions: class for parsing version information
tinyxml: XML parser for input files
Utils: contains Timer class, used to measure performance

To get started, read "Getting Started.docx".

